{"tid":943690,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"其實TVB班演員個個演技咁屎, 點解啲豬肉獎都可以傾成十幾個post?","createTime":"2018-12-16T16:02:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T17:42:05.000Z","uid":67294,"like":38,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e454559511aef01bc6001d01a411c3bd58c38fda","tid":943690,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T16:02:43.000Z","msg":"TVB劇無劇本, 演員又無演技<br />\n根本成個TVB啲人都係小學雞level, 呢個頒獎禮根本邊個拎視帝視后都WFC<br />\n你睇子華神拎果年都係得啖笑, 拎完之後第二年都係去拍電影<br />\n因為佢根本都不屑個視帝獎, 想做一啲真係高質既野出黎<br />\n<br />\n明明個獎1. 無公信力, 2. 本身套電視劇己經低質, 3. 候選人實力參差<br />\n拎個獎都可以討論成十幾頁, 仲要話邊個邊個先應該拎<br />\n當正自己係專家咁, 講真有少少智商都唔會理邊個拎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ca78395c568fedb81dac72c405b1291c4631c2","tid":943690,"uid":168366,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T16:03:48.000Z","msg":"去到今日都可以用埋d垃圾佈景<br />\n到今時今日仲可以個窗一望就知係假 <br />\n餐廳一望就知係假<br />\n搵真單位同餐廳拍係咪咁撚難? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5d0f04dcd14ae5442e3013136f79817cd7adfe7","tid":943690,"uid":38904,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T16:04:31.000Z","msg":"乜嘢質素嘅人咪鍾意睇乜嘢質素嘅嘢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab4a7b6f0c3422d7e2d763c73c970bc561ea82f","tid":943690,"uid":67294,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b0ca78395c568fedb81dac72c405b1291c4631c2","tid":943690,"uid":168366,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T16:03:48.000Z","msg":"去到今日都可以用埋d垃圾佈景<br />\n到今時今日仲可以個窗一望就知係假 <br />\n餐廳一望就知係假<br />\n搵真單位同餐廳拍係咪咁撚難? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T16:05:16.000Z","msg":"餐廳唔係假, 不過係TVB入面既canteen黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hk